# Week 13: Must-Win Scenarios

## Required Inputs
- `{league_name}` - Name of the fantasy league
- `{week_number}` - Week 13
- `{selected_tone}` - User's chosen tone
- `{uploaded_data}` - Current standings and remaining schedules

## Prompt Template

Write 200-word elimination scenarios in {selected_tone} tone.

[IF BANTER]: Playful pressure - "No pressure, but lose and your season's over. Sleep tight!"
[IF BRUTAL]: Harsh reality - "Win or go home, and based on your roster, start packing"
[IF PROFESSIONAL]: Clear scenarios - "Team A clinches with win + Team B loss OR..."
[IF CINEMATIC]: Do or die drama - "Everything has led to this moment... survive or perish"
[IF CASUAL]: Straightforward - "Here's what needs to happen for you to make playoffs"

Detail exact scenarios for each bubble team, make the stakes clear.

## Key Elements
- List each bubble team's scenario
- Include win-and-in situations
- Include elimination scenarios
- Explain tiebreaker situations

